title: Big Fish Games: Super Stamp
description:
Have fun collecting a wide variety of stamps by matching 
           shapes in Super Stamp. Did you know that the first official 
           stamp, the Penny Black, was introduced in the year 1840 by 
           Great Britain? Find out more exciting stamp facts and enjoy  
           beautifully drawn stamp collecting in this great Puzzle inlay 
           game.

           * Collect tons of stamps
           * Beautiful graphics
           * Win trophies and awards
